ree:\n\n```\nCaused by: java.lang.RuntimeException: unexpected\n    at com.github.davidmoten.rtree.fbs.SerializerFlatBuffers.readFully(SerializerFlatBuffers.java:165)\n    at com.github.davidmoten.rtree.fbs.SerializerFlatBuffers.read(SerializerFlatBuffers.java:123)\n```\n\nThe error occurs here:\n\n```\n    @VisibleForTesting\n    static byte[] readFully(InputStream is, int numBytes) throws IOException {\n        byte[] b = new byte[numBytes];\n        int n = is.read(b);\n        if (n != numBytes)\n            throw new RuntimeException(\"unexpected\");\n        return b;\n    }\n```\n\nI believe the contract of InputStream.read(byte[]) does not always do full reads, there should be some form of loop here to retry. I've seen such errors before.\n\nDo let me know if I'm missing something.\n","closed_by":{"login":"eadwright","id":17048626,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE3MDQ4NjI2","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/17048626?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/eadwright","html_url":"https://github.com/eadwright","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/eadwright/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/eadwright/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/eadwright/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/eadwright/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/eadwright/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/eadwright/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/eadwright/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/eadwright/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/eadwright/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/davidmoten/rtree/issues/50/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/davidmoten/